    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Endophallus of male genitalia for Parena spp. showing the definition of endophallic structures, dorsal (d) and leftlateral (l) views. A P. (Bothynoptera) tripunctata (Bates), modified from Fig. 39B. B P. (Crossoglossa) laesipennis (Bates), modified from Fig. 18A. C P. (Parena) bicolor Motschulsky, modified from Fig. 51A. D P. (Parena) picipes sp. n., modified from Fig. 63. Blue, primary sclerite; Magenta, apical sclerite; Green, squamate sheath; Yellow, squamate sac." ;
